               <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_I_801"><rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="pe__siegfried_QGW_II_I_800">Seifrid, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien-st_peter-altar_st_maria-messe_straiherin">chaplan</roleName> der von Frau Chlar der Straiherinne hinz sand Peter
